{"tid":89206,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗：優化長生津或令結構性財赤提早","createTime":"2017-01-21T07:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T08:12:58.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b7d037ae1ddd2f3255a5450369489a954b9a817","tid":89206,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T07:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/CS.WELFARE.1300.2101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FCS.WELFARE.1300.2101.jpg&h=2b5bad6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】政務司司長張建宗承認優化長者生活津貼後，可能令政府結構性財赤提早於2026年出現。他重申未來5至6年不用加稅，又透露取消綜援「衰仔紙」安排，最快可在農曆新年假期後實施。<br />\n<br />\n施政報告提出優化長者生活津貼，政府預計首年額外要用多65億元，未來十年平均每年用多76億元。<br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗承認，政府可能因此提前於2026年出現結構性財赤長遠要考慮改革稅制。<br />\n<br />\n政府稍後就優化長生津向財委會申請撥款。<br />\n<br />\n他又說取消綜援「衰仔紙」安排，屬於行政措施，最快可在農曆年初六、初七推行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=208044\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D208044&d=kSqNWZ1VzRrKxwNx86kb2wv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=a76a5944\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D208044&h=b619e9c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=208044</a>"},{"pid":"9fb1b3e6ffaa0341ea2d84269556d8c8f9a80303","tid":89206,"uid":71744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T07:48:17.000Z","msg":"長生津貼 = 長壽者有政府補助<br />\n長者生活津貼 = 政府資助長者使費<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報紙佬真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8838bae464c43eed9d2910c78bda5f48fb8ce0dd","tid":89206,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T07:49:50.000Z","msg":"優你老母化"},{"pid":"fa8cd57c013695b76b5305d12119c0eb3eb26a6f","tid":89206,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T07:56:04.000